# Student Performance Prediction

##  Project Overview
This project predicts whether a student will **pass or fail** based on study hours using machine learning classification algorithms.

##  Technologies Used
- Python  
- NumPy  
- Matplotlib  
- Scikit-learn  

##  Project Steps
1. Data Preparation  
2. Data Visualization  
3. Model Training  
4. Model Evaluation  
5. Prediction Visualization  

##  Models Used
- Logistic Regression  
- Decision Tree Classifier  

##  Results
The models were evaluated using **accuracy score** and **graphs** showing predicted probabilities and decision boundaries.
Accuracy

| Metric    | Value |
| --------- | ----- |
| Accuracy  | 90%   |
| Precision | 83%   |
| Recall    | 100%  |
| F1-score  | 91%   |
